---
title: Aloo Gobi Lagoon Stew with Cauliflower, Green Beans and Yoghurt
description: Make tasty waves at dinnertime with this delicious water-inspired Aloo Gobi Lagoon Stew.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W28_UK_F14751-2_Main__7low-5f8a496a.jpg
